---
title: Seed-Crusted Turkey with Bulgur Salad
description: Chewy, earthy bulgur is the perfect vessel for these seed-crusted turkey tenders. This salad is packed full of goodness, including cucumbers, tomatoes, spring mix and feta.

Ingredients: Turkey breast • Bulgur wheat (durum wheat semolina) (wheat) • Roma tomatoes • Cucumber • Spring mix (lolla rosa multi-leaf lettuce, red flash red oak lettuce, red leaf multi-leaf lettuce, green oak lettuce, bally hoo tango lettuce) • Mayonnaise  (canola and/or soy oil, liquid whole egg, frozen egg yolk, water, salt, sugar, vinegar, concentrated lemon juice, spice extract, mustard, lactic acid, calcium disodium EDTA) (mustard, egg) • White wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium metabisulfite) (sulphites) • Feta cheese (pasteurized milk, partly skimmed milk, water, salt, lipase, bacterial culture, microbial enzyme, cellulose, natamycin, calcium chloride) (milk) • Seed blend (sunflower seeds, pepitas, soybean oil and/or canola oil) • Panko breadcrumbs (bleached wheat flour, yeast, sugar, salt) (wheat).
